abled, revision shortlinks will render the revision content directly for logged-out visitors instead of redirecting to the preview URL.'=>'Ni aiyipada, PublishPress Revisions dènà awọn alejo lati wo awọn iworan atunṣe. Nigbati o ba mu ṣiṣẹ, shortlinks atunṣe yoo fi akoonu atunṣe han taara fun awọn alejo ti o ti forukọsilẹ silẹ dipo gbigbe si URL iworan.','Dummy'=>'Dummy','No post types configured yet. Click "Add Post Type" to get started.'=>'Ko si awọn iru ifiweranṣẹ ti a ṣe eto sibẹsibẹ. Tẹ "Fi Iru Ifiweranṣẹ Kun" lati bẹrẹ.','Add Post Type'=>'Fi Iru Ifiweranṣẹ Kun','Log entry deleted successfully.'=>'Tí ìròyìn ti paṣẹ ni aṣeyọri.','%d log entries deleted successfully.'=>'%d ìròyìn ti paṣẹ ni aṣeyọri.','All logs have been cleared.'=>'Gbogbo awọn ìròyìn ni a ti nu.','Title'=>'Akole','Details'=>'Alaye','Are you sure you want to delete this log entry?'=>'Ṣé o dájú pé o fẹ pa ìròyìn yìí run?','Tablet'=>'Tablet','Mobile'=>'Mobile','Desktop'=>'Desktop','%1$s from %2$s visited at %3$s'=>'%1$s lati %2$s ṣabẹwo ni %3$s','%1$s visited at %2$s'=>'%1$s ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','From %1$s, visited at %2$s'=>'Lati %1$s, ṣabẹwo ni %2$s','Visited at %s'=>'Ṣabẹwo ni %s','via %s'=>'nipasẹ %s','Edit shortlink settings'=>'Ṣatunkọ awọn eto asopọ kukuru','Target url not found.'=>'A ko ri url ibi-afẹde.','Invalid URL scheme. Only http, https, ftp, ftps, and mailto are allowed.'=>'Ilana URL ti ko tọ. Kii ṣe http, https, ftp, ftps, ati mailto ni a gba laaye.','Invalid URL.'=>'URL ti ko tọ.','Tiny slug could not created.'=>'A ko le ṣẹda slug kekere.','Link - %s'=>'Asopọ - %s','Shortlink will appear here'=>'Asopọ kukuru yoo han nibi','Enter a long URL and make a shortlink'=>'Tẹ url gigun kan ki o ṣẹda asopọ kukuru','Long URL'=>'URL Gigun','Close'=>'Pa','Create Shortlink'=>'Ṣẹda Asopọ Kukuru','Reset Today\'s Analytics'=>'Tun awọn itupalẹ Ọjọ́ yìí ṣe','Reset Week\'s Analytics'=>'Tun awọn itupalẹ Ọsẹ yìí ṣe','Reset Month\'s Analytics'=>'Tun awọn itupalẹ Oṣù yìí ṣe','Reset Year\'s Analytics'=>'Tun awọn i